<div class="container">
  <div class="container" style="width: 75%; margin: 0 auto;">
        
    <h1>Peer Allies</h1>
    <h3>We are a support network of students that hold weekly "office hours" to provide an opportunity for survivors of sexual violence or harassment who may have felt powerless to talk, be heard, and be believed, as well as provide information to survivors in a safe space about other resources both on and off campus.</h3>
    
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>

    <p>Each of the allies currently holds an office hour every week.  If, however, you would like to set up a meeting with an ally that doesn't fall within one of the available office hours, please click on the button below.</p>
    
    <%= link_to crisis_info_path, class: 'btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary' do%>
    <%= "Connect with an Ally"%>
    <% end %>
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
    <p>If you would like to look at the weekly calendar to see which allies are available during official office hours, please click below.</p>
    
    <%= link_to calendar_path, class: 'btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary' do%>
    <%= "View the Allies' Calendar"%>
    <% end %>
    
  </div>
</div>